    Title: I Ching
  Title: The Man of Many Qualities
Title: Acquiring Experience
---
There is an inevitability about the progress of youth. The older generation
thinks it understands youth, but it does not. Despite the perilous conditions
surrounding the inexperienced stage of the young man's life and the
intermittent halting of his advances, success will be achieved. Like water
overlowing in time, all pitfalls are eventually overcome.
